OL,3,C'Calm before the storm': Inflation
OL,4,Cfalls to 2.6% ahead of April's rising
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FUK inflation has fallen to 2.6%, but
OL,8,Feconomists have warned this is the
OL,9,F"calm before the storm" of April's
OL,10,Frising bills.
OL,12,FIt represents a second consecutive dip
OL,13,Fafter inflation eased by more than
OL,14,Fexpected to 2.8% in February on the
OL,15,Fback of lower clothing prices.
OL,17,FNevertheless, the rate is still higher
OL,18,Fthan the 2% target set by the Bank of
OL,19,FEngland and the government.
