OL,3,C'Calm before the storm': Inflation
OL,4,Cfalls to 2.6% ahead of April's rising
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThe good news for consumers could be
OL,8,Fshort-lived however as higher bills
OL,9,Fhit households in April which could
OL,10,Faffect next month's figures.
OL,12,FSpeaking on Wednesday, Chancellor
OL,13,FRachel Reeves said: "Inflation falling
OL,14,Ffor two months in a row, wages growing
OL,15,Ffaster than prices, and positive
OL,16,Fgrowth figures are encouraging signs
OL,17,Fthat our plan for change is working,
OL,18,Fbut there is more to be done.
