OL,3,C'Calm before the storm': Inflation
OL,4,Cfalls to 2.6% ahead of April's rising
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,F"I know many families are still
OL,8,Fstruggling with the cost of living and
OL,9,Fthis is an anxious time because of a
OL,10,Fchanging world.
OL,12,F"That is why the Government has
OL,13,Fboosted pay for three million people
OL,14,Fby increasing the minimum wage, frozen
OL,15,Ffuel duty and begun rolling out free
OL,16,Fbreakfast clubs in primary schools."
OL,18,FThe decrease has been largely
OL,19,Fattributed to a fall in petrol prices.
