OL,3,C'Calm before the storm': Inflation
OL,4,Cfalls to 2.6% ahead of April's rising
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FRobert Wood, chief UK economist at
OL,8,FPantheon Macroeconomics, said: "Weekly
OL,9,Fmotor fuels price data point to a 1.1%
OL,10,Fmonth-to-month fall, well below the
OL,11,F1.9% gain a year ago.
OL,13,F"A base effect from alcohol and
OL,14,Ftobacco prices a year ago should
OL,15,Fsubtract another three basis points
OL,16,F(0.03 percentage points) from headline
OL,17,FCPI inflation."
