OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FHe added that the potential reduction
OL,8,Fin price rises would be "the calm
OL,9,Fbefore the storm of April price hikes,
OL,10,Fwhich should drive up headline
OL,11,Finflation to 3.6%".
OL,13,FThe Bank of England has also said
OL,14,Finflation is likely to increase
OL,15,Fthrough this year and peak at around
OL,16,F3.7% later this summer.
