OL,3,C'Calm before the storm': Inflation
OL,4,Cfalls to 2.6% ahead of April's rising
OL,5,Cbills
OL,7,FThe figure will be the last inflation
OL,8,Freading that the Bank's monetary
OL,9,Fpolicy committee will receive before
OL,10,Fthey vote on whether to reduce
OL,11,Finterest rates ` which currently sits
OL,12,Fat 4.5% ` at their meeting next month.
OL,14,FThe news comes at a time when the
OL,15,Fglobal economy is wrestling with an
OL,16,Funcertain future as the US President
OL,17,Fseeks to reshape international trade
OL,18,Fand economies with sweeping tariffs.
